snippet.title: Bubble Shooter DX - PlayStation 4 Gameplay
snippet.description:
Bubble Shooter DX is a classic bubble shoot game.

This addictive classic bubble blast match-three game comes with clean and modern graphics, hundreds of
great challenging levels and some nice special items for better game experience in harder levels.

Developed by EntwicklerX
Published by THOMAS CLAUS UND FRANK MENZEL
Also released on Nintendo Switch and Android (Google Play Store / itch.io)

#ps4 #playstation4 #theforeseenarcade #bubbleshooter #bubbleshootergames #bubbleshooterdx #entwicklerx
